# ======================================
# Setup Instructions
# ======================================

# 1. MongoDB Setup:
#    - Install MongoDB locally OR use MongoDB Atlas (cloud)
#    - Create a database named 'taskhub'
#    - Update MONGODB_URI with your connection string

# 2. Email Setup (Gmail):
#    - Go to Google Account settings
#    - Enable 2-Factor Authentication
#    - Generate an App Password: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
#    - Use this app password in EMAIL_PASSWORD

# 3. Twilio Setup (SMS):
#    - Sign up at https://www.twilio.com
#    - Get your Account SID and Auth Token from Console
#    - Get a Twilio phone number for sending SMS
#    - Add these credentials above

# 4. JWT Secret:
#    - Generate a secure random string:
#      node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"
#    - Replace JWT_SECRET with the generated string

# 5. Find Your Local IP (for mobile testing):
#    - Windows: ipconfig (look for IPv4 Address)
#    - Mac/Linux: ifconfig or ip addr show
#    - Update EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL with your local IP